English
Rumors of Wars is a film with two converging story-lines, the first one centering
around an aspiring college journalist named Roxy (Jennifer Cooper), finds herself
searching for answers when she investigates end time prophecies for a term paper.
Recording her research in a diary, her findings prove to have more of an impact
than she could have ever imagined. Her diary is discovered years later, in the
rubble of a post apocalypse society filled with decay and violence. With the truth
of what really happened to the world in its pages, the book finds its way into to
the hands of an officer, named Shaw (Ben Davies) in the New World Army. But what
will he do with this new found truth?
